annotation.text:
This app leverages Google AutoML to do Natural Language Classification. https://cloud.google.com/natural-language/automl/docs/
The steps are: 1. Upload dataset to Google's Cloud Storage. 2. Import dataset from Cloud Storage into Google's AutoML. 3. Train a model. 4. Deploy the model
